{"id":"5663","name":"bright-early-its-the-sun-edition","title":"Bright &amp; Early: It&#x2019;s The Sun Edition","author":"Christy Frink","date":"2010-09-03T10:00:00-05:00","tags":["28th avenue connector","autumn","debt","dui","fall","indian tribes","labor day","labor day weekend","lotus energy drink","nashville flood","native americans","new orleans saints","operation photo rescue","photo restoration","sobriety checkpoints","tennessee commission on indian affairs","titans","weather","zero tolerance"],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/greystgirl/4200931451/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2685/4200931451_6db9f52915.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"416\" height=\"278\"></a></p><p>Good morning, Nashville. <a href=\"http://nashvillewx.com/2010/09/a-little-rain-a-lot-cooler/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillewx.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">We just can&#x2019;t help but get a little giddy when we check out the weekend weather report, which is currently calling for 70s and sunshine tomorrow</a>. Overnight and early morning temperatures will dip into the 50s with higher elevations possibly even seeing some 40s. All we have to do is get through a few pop-up showers around noon and we&#x2019;ll be golden for the rest of the weekend.</p><ul><li><strong>Debt-free is the way to be.</strong> Out of 50 states and Washington, DC, Tennessee ranks dead last in debt. As in, <a href=\"http://wpln.org/?p=20125\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;wpln.org&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">we currently borrow less money than any other state in the country</a>.</li><li><strong>Indian tribes lose recognition. </strong><a href=\"http://www.fox17.com/template/inews_wire/wires.regional.tn/3c129a17-www.fox17.com.shtml\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.fox17.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Six Indian tribes will lose their state recognition as a result of a lawsuit against the Tennessee Commission on Indian Affairs</a> because the commission violated open meeting laws when voting to recognize the tribes in June. The commission is also now defunct.</li><li><strong>Zero tolerance.</strong> The State Troopers would like to remind everyone that <a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/global/story.asp?s=13087868\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">they won&#x2019;t be tolerating any sort of driving under the influence over the holiday weekend and they&#x2019;ll have sobriety checkpoints set up all over the place</a>. So call (or <a href=\"http://www.gofastcab.com/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.gofastcab.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">text</a>!) a cab, call your mom or do whatever you need to do to find a safe ride home.</li><li><strong>Bits &amp; pieces. </strong>The <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20100902/PROMO/100902094/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Titans toppled the Saints last night</a>, but it was awfully close &#x2026; We&#x2019;re not shy about loving all things local, and <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/global/story.asp?s=13094366\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">now there&#x2019;s even a local energy drink</a> &#x2026; The <a href=\"http://nashvillecitypaper.com/content/city-news/proposal-connect-west-end-and-north-nashville-back-table?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed:+NashvilleCityPaper-CityNews+(Nashville+City+Paper+-+City+News)&amp;utm_content=Google+Reader\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">28th Avenue Connector concept</a> is back in the running &#x2026; Operation Photo Rescue will be in town next week to <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20100903/COLUMNIST0128/9030320/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">help flood victims restore flood-damaged photos</a>.</li></ul><p><em>Photo by </em><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/greystgirl/4200931451/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Grey Street Girl</em></a><em>.</em></p><p>No related posts.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}